data.description:
Centrally located darling Bungalow that is move-in ready! 
The Living Room features a cozy window seat surrounded by built-ins and tons of natural light throughout.  Walk through the arch doorways to the kitchen which has beautiful dark wood countertops, open air shelving, newer kitchen floors and added cabinetry and counters for storage and prep space.  Two bedrooms located on the main with a third loft bedroom.  
Out back awaits your private oasis with a pergola, deck, entertainment space and firepit to enjoy both day and evening outdoors.  Raised garden beds are ready for planting with a storage shed to store all of your lawn and garden supplies.
Located close to the Farmer's Market, The ARC, groceries and shopping.
